<div id='api-docs'>
  <h3>API Reference</h3>

  <p>To use the Alloy API, you will make a simple <code>post</code> request to <code>http://alloy.divshot.com/compile/:lang</code>, where
    <code>:lang</code> is one of <code>sass</code>, <code>scss</code>, <code>less</code>, or <code>stylus</code>. The request can either be of type <code>applicaton/json</code> or <code>application/x-www-form-encoded</code> and must include a <code>source</code> parameter
    with the uncompiled code.</p>

  <h4>Example</h4>

  <pre><code>POST http://alloy.divshot.com/compile/sass
Content-Type: application/json

{"source":"@import \"compass\"\n\n.btn\n  @mixin border-radius(15px)\n  background-color: blue"}</code></div>